caption.p: Pathway analyses of NS1 interacting host factors. DAVID-Panther analyses of ( A) biological processes, ( B) molecular functions and ( C) reactome and Kyoto Encyclopedia of Genes and Genomes (KEGG) pathways. Gene Ontologies of ( D) Biological processes and ( E) Molecular functions. STRING analyses of NS1-interacting proteins in ( F) Gene expression pathway, ( G) Processing of capped intron-containing pre-mRNA pathway, and ( H) Spliceosome pathway.
